          "_name": "people07",
          "_sourceTheme": "startm5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"people07\" group=\"People\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"6\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"6\">\n        <input type=\"range\" name=\"textWidth\" title=\"Width\" min=\"4\" max=\"12\" value=\"8\" step=\"1\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Image\" name=\"showImage\" checked>\n        <select title=\"Image Align\" name=\"contentAlign\">\n          <option value=\"justify-content-start\">Left</option>\n          <option value=\"justify-content-center\" selected>Center</option>\n          <option value=\"justify-content-end\">Right</option>\n        </select>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Name\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" name=\"bgColor\" value=\"#ffffff\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"col-md-12 col-lg-{{textWidth}}\">\n                <p class=\"card-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".card-text\">Privacy Policy<br><br>At Purenura and Spirituras, your privacy is our top priority. We are committed to protecting your personal information and ensuring a transparent experience on our platform.<br><br>1. Data Collection and Storage<br>We believe in absolute data privacy. Our website does not collect, store, or sell any of your personal or financial information. You can browse our content with complete peace of mind, knowing your data remains entirely yours.<br><br>2. Third-Party and Affiliate Links<br>To support our community and provide you with recommended resources, our platform contains affiliate links. When you click on these links to make a purchase:<br><br>You will be safely redirected to secure, encrypted third-party vendor platforms.<br><br>We do not have access to any transaction details, payment methods, or personal information entered on those external sites.<br><br>3. External Privacy Policies<br>Please note that these external third-party websites operate independently and have their own distinct privacy policies. We encourage you to review the privacy terms of any third-party site you visit, as we do not assume responsibility or liability for their content and activities.<br><br>4. Your Consent<br>By continuing to use our website and services, you hereby acknowledge and agree to the terms outlined in this Privacy Policy.<br></p>\n                <div class=\"img-wrapper mt-4 {{contentAlign}}\" mbr-if=\"showImage\">\n                    <img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/f07303ab-848f-4ef4-9c54-1f6215f5f209-240x240.webp\" alt data-slide-to=\"0\" data-bs-slide-to=\"0\">\n                </div>\n                <p class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style mt-3\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title, .img-wrapper\">@purenura</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
