          "_name": "people07",
          "_sourceTheme": "startm5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"people07\" group=\"People\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"6\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"1\">\n        <input type=\"range\" name=\"textWidth\" title=\"Width\" min=\"4\" max=\"12\" value=\"8\" step=\"1\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Image\" name=\"showImage\" checked>\n        <select title=\"Image Align\" name=\"contentAlign\">\n          <option value=\"justify-content-start\">Left</option>\n          <option value=\"justify-content-center\" selected>Center</option>\n          <option value=\"justify-content-end\">Right</option>\n        </select>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Name\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" name=\"bgColor\" value=\"#ffffff\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"col-md-12 col-lg-{{textWidth}}\">\n                <p class=\"card-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".card-text\">Terms &amp; Conditions<br><br>Welcome to our platform. By accessing and using Purenura and Spirituras, you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agree to be bound by the following terms and conditions.<br><br>1. General Nature of Our Platform<br>Our website serves as an informational and promotional platform dedicated to wellness, personal balance, and spiritual growth. We provide curated recommendations, insights, and content to support your personal journey.<br><br>2. Affiliate Disclosure and Commissions<br>To keep our platform running and provide free content, we participate in affiliate marketing programs.<br><br>This website contains affiliate links to selected products and services.<br><br>If you choose to make a purchase through these links, we may earn a small commission at absolutely no additional cost to you.<br><br>3. Third-Party Products and Liability<br>Please note that we do not directly sell, manufacture, or ship any products.<br><br>All product claims, specifications, guarantees, and refund requests are handled solely and exclusively by the official third-party vendor.<br><br>Any customer service issues, returns, or dispute resolutions must be directed to the vendor from whom the product was purchased.<br><br>4. No Medical or Professional Advice<br>The content provided on this website—including text, graphics, recommendations, and other materials—is for informational and educational purposes only.<br><br>It is not intended to be a substitute for professional medical advice, diagnosis, or treatment.<br><br>Always seek the advice of your physician, spiritual guide, or other qualified professionals with any questions you may have regarding a medical or personal condition.<br><br>5. Changes to These Terms<br>We reserve the right to update or modify these Terms &amp; Conditions at any time without prior notice. Your continued use of the website following any changes constitutes your acceptance of the revised terms.<br></p>\n                <div class=\"img-wrapper mt-4 {{contentAlign}}\" mbr-if=\"showImage\">\n                    <img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/f07303ab-848f-4ef4-9c54-1f6215f5f209-240x240.webp\" alt data-slide-to=\"0\" data-bs-slide-to=\"0\">\n                </div>\n                <p class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style mt-3\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title, .img-wrapper\">@purenura</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
