          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"features031\" group=\"Article\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-fullscreen': fullScreen, 'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"6\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"6\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Reverse\" name=\"reverseContent\" checked>\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\">\n        <input type=\"range\" name=\"imageWidth\" title=\"Image\" min=\"4\" max=\"8\" step=\"1\" value=\"4\">\n        <header>Card</header>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Card BG\" name=\"cardbg\" value=\"#ffffff\" selected>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Card Color\" name=\"cardbg\" value=\"#ffffff\" selected>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Icon Color\" name=\"iconColor\" value=\"#9fe870\" selected>\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\">\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#ffffff\" selected>\n            <input type=\"video\" title=\"Video\" value=\"https://vimeo.com/428046504\">\n        </fieldset>\n        <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n        <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.7\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n    <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type!== 'color'\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': overlayColor}\"></div>\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\" mbr-if=\"showTitle || showText\">\n            <div class=\"col-md-12 content-head mb-5\">\n                <h1 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style  mb-0\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\"><b>Benefits Of The Genius Switch</b></h1>\n                <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mt-4 mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn\">\n                    Great for pro-coders for fast prototyping and small customers' projects.\n                </p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center  blockContent\">\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-lg\">\n                <div class=\"item-wrapper align-left\">\n                    <div class=\"counter-container mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" data-multiline mbr-article>\n                        <ul>\n                            <li><b>Science-Based Brainwave Technology: Built on proven neuroscience principles, The Genius Switch uses binaural beats and isochronic tones to safely and naturally stimulate brainwave activity. This helps your brain enter states of focus, creativity, and deep relaxation with ease.\n</b></li><li><b>Effortless and Easy to Use: No need for complicated meditation or self-help methods. Just press play, listen, and let the audio frequencies do the work. It’s perfect for beginners or anyone with a busy lifestyle.\n</b></li><li><b>Enhances Focus, Creativity &amp; Productivity: The targeted sound frequencies are designed to boost mental focus, support problem-solving, and unlock creative thinking—ideal for work, study, or personal projects.\n</b></li><li><b>Reduces Stress &amp; Promotes Emotional Balance: Relaxing soundscapes help calm your nervous system, reducing stress, anxiety, and emotional overwhelm. Many users feel more balanced and at peace after each session.\n</b></li><li><b>Delivers Fast, Noticeable Results: Many users report feeling sharper, calmer, and more focused after just a few sessions. Regular use amplifies these benefits over time.\n</b></li><li><b>Customizable for Your Personal Goals: With a variety of sessions available, you can choose the audio that best fits your mental state or daily goal—whether it's boosting creativity, winding down, or staying alert.\n</b></li><li><b>Risk-Free with Money-Back Guarantee: Most packages offer a 100% money-back guarantee, giving you the chance to try The Genius Switch with zero risk.</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li>\n                        </ul>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-{{imageWidth}}\">\n                <div class=\"image-wrapper\">\n                    <img class=\"w-100\" src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/untitled-design.webp\" alt>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
