          "_name": "features031",
          "_sourceTheme": "startm5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"features031\" group=\"Article\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-fullscreen': fullScreen, 'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"6\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"6\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Reverse\" name=\"reverseContent\" checked>\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\">\n        <input type=\"range\" name=\"imageWidth\" title=\"Image\" min=\"4\" max=\"8\" step=\"1\" value=\"4\">\n        <header>Card</header>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Card BG\" name=\"cardbg\" value=\"#ffffff\" selected>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Card Color\" name=\"cardbg\" value=\"#ffffff\" selected>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Icon Color\" name=\"iconColor\" value=\"#9fe870\" selected>\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\">\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#ffffff\" selected>\n            <input type=\"video\" title=\"Video\" value=\"https://vimeo.com/428046504\">\n        </fieldset>\n        <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n        <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.7\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n    <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type!== 'color'\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': overlayColor}\"></div>\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\" mbr-if=\"showTitle || showText\">\n            <div class=\"col-md-12 content-head mb-5\">\n                <h1 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style  mb-0\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\"><b>Benefits of Billionaire Brain Wave</b></h1>\n                <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mt-4 mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn\">\n                    Great for pro-coders for fast prototyping and small customers' projects.\n                </p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center  blockContent\">\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-lg\">\n                <div class=\"item-wrapper align-left\">\n                    <div class=\"counter-container mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" data-multiline mbr-article>\n                        <ul>\n                            <li><b>Wealth Magnetism - Attracts financial opportunities by aligning your subconscious with prosperity frequencies. It eliminates scarcity friction, making wealth attraction an effortless, natural habit.\n</b></li><li><b>Stress Elimination - Reduces money stress by lowering cortisol and inducing calm Theta states. It replaces financial panic with the mental clarity needed for productive, high-level solutions.\n</b></li><li><b>Sharpened Intuition - Sharpens financial instincts for superior business and investment decisions. It heightens subconscious awareness, allowing you to sense profitable opportunities with precision.\n</b></li><li><b>Creative Breakthroughs - Unlocks billionaire-level ideation by accessing untapped cognitive potential. It triggers advanced problem-solving and the creative breakthroughs required for market leadership.\n</b></li><li><b>Confidence Boost - Dissolves self-doubt through neural reprogramming, installing unshakable belief in your success. It replaces hesitation with the absolute certainty of a top-tier performer.\n</b></li><li><b>Manifestation Power - Accelerates goal realization by bridging the gap between focused intention and subconscious alignment. It hardwires your mind to recognize and execute the exact actions required to turn ambitious visions into tangible success.\n</b></li><li><b>Mental Clarity - Eliminates brain fog to grant you laser-sharp financial perception. This module sharpens your sensory processing, allowing you to identify profitable opportunities and market inefficiencies that others overlook.\n</b></li><li><b>Emotional Balance - Maintains emotional equilibrium during financial volatility by regulating your stress response at the neural level. It prevents panic-driven errors, ensuring you respond to market challenges with the calculated composure of an elite leader.\n</b></li><li><b>Faster Learning - Accelerates financial learning through optimized neuroplasticity. It allows you to master complex investment systems and wealth strategies with rapid speed and permanent retention.\n</b></li><li><b>Relationship Harmony - Harmonizes financial partnerships by fostering a shared abundance mindset. It neutralizes money-related conflict and aligns collective goals through unified subconscious frequencies.\n</b></li><li><b>Health Benefits - Lowers stress-related symptoms via regular Theta-state relaxation. It triggers whole-body recovery by neutralizing the physiological effects of chronic financial pressure and physical fatigue.\n</b></li><li><b>Time Efficiency - Delivers peak results in just 7 minutes daily, eliminating the need for long meditation sessions. It makes high-performance wealth reprogramming accessible to even the most time-constrained professionals.\n</b></li><li><b>Each benefit builds on neuroscience principles to create compound effects - the more you use it, the stronger the results become. Perfect for entrepreneurs, investors, and anyone ready to upgrade their financial blueprint permanently.</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li><li><b>\n</b></li>\n                        </ul>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-{{imageWidth}}\">\n                <div class=\"image-wrapper\">\n                    <img class=\"w-100\" src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/airbrush-image-enhancer-1784482534337.webp\" alt>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
